## Problem
The company needed a clear view of sales across products and regions.

## Dataset
- 12 months of sales data (~5,000 rows) in Excel
- Cleaned with Power Query (duplicates removed, missing values fixed)

## Approach
- Built DAX measures for KPIs: Total Sales, Profit Margin, YTD Growth
- Created interactive slicers (Region, Product, Month)
- Added drilldowns for managers to track performance by team

